           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npt    not  < w-cnt-sts-imp-mpt
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-tes      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se la pagina attuale e' la massima  *
      *                          * si va' ad accettazione corpo        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npt    not  < w-cnt-sts-imp-mpt
                     move  w-cnt-sts-imp-svp
                                          to   w-cnt-sts-imp-npt
                     go to acc-nok-reg-300.
