      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      w-cat-rig-max        to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           move      w-rig                to   w-cat-rig-buf          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
